{"tid":987164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳門料理　似曾相識又非常陌生","createTime":"2019-01-19T05:45:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T00:37:37.000Z","uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"686df20f60f566440bd7e734906471d8c9b433d3","tid":987164,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T05:45:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10155570816162357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10155570816162357&d=G3JivrrVtvrQN9YN3IyjfjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=d9587106\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10155570816162357</a><br />\n<br />\nKevin Ho<br />\n<br />\n如果香港俾葡國統治幾百年，大概我哋依家係食緊馬介休，摩囉雞飯，乾炒免治牛肉飯，薯蓉湯，杏仁批，炸青豆(傳到日本變天婦羅)。<br />\n<br />\n就連廣東麵都會變成落咖哩醬，好似澳門咁。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/macaohongkong/photos/a.1826647857569561/1852843481616665/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmacaohongkong%2Fphotos%2Fa.1826647857569561%2F1852843481616665%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=G3JivrrVtvrQN9YN3IyjfjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=722ae8d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/macaohongkong/photos/a.1826647857569561/1852843481616665/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n乾免治牛肉飯-一種澳門茶餐廳常見嘅食品，由牛肉粒+薯仔粒+洋蔥干炒之後再加上一隻煎蛋組合而成嘅一個飯。其實炒出嚟係幾香口嘅，不過如果係冇汁不歡嘅人就唔太適合啦，因為佢真係要炒得好乾身先至好食。<br />\n<br />\n#乾免治牛肉飯 #干免牛<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/vuVWPU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FvuVWPU&h=446050fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDaniel Palillo 真正土生葡人o既乾免治，係要炒到細細粒好似芝麻咁細，如果大粒到肉粒咁，就只係一般茶記<br />\n<br />\nNg William 絕對香港 冇嘅嘢 食<br />\n<br />\nChilds Chow 正宗讀法：「乾mean嘔飯」<br />\n<br />\n方丈 免牛澳門一般乾濕都有得食<br />\n<br />\nMargaret Fiona Ngai 最鐘意澳門飲凍飲 比支糖水你自己較甜度<br />\n<br />\nKeanu Chung 一直認知免牛係碎牛肉<br />\n<br />\nBilly Au 我曾比人反問「有乾ga咩」？<br />\n<br />\nTensaki Shinkin 冇汁不歡<br />\n<br />\n謝飛賴 我剛到澳門做嘢，冇為意個&ldquo;干&rdquo;字，叫左免治牛，佢又冇理我，到左之後我問佢咩來?<img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/td0/1/16/1f602.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fimages%2Femoji.php%2Fv9%2Ftd0%2F1%2F16%2F1f602.png&h=5ffc90d5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/td0/1/16/1f602.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fimages%2Femoji.php%2Fv9%2Ftd0%2F1%2F16%2F1f602.png&h=5ffc90d5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/td0/1/16/1f602.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fimages%2Femoji.php%2Fv9%2Ftd0%2F1%2F16%2F1f602.png&h=5ffc90d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMira Fenrietta 以前有間餐廳會落葡腸絲，不過已經成為絕響囉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nJoe Da Fabian 有濕免治牛飯<br />\n<br />\n港澳小不同 係完全唔同嘅食物<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20171107121604/http://blog.billyau.com/posts/944\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20171107121604%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fblog.billyau.com%2Fposts%2F944&d=G3JivrrVtvrQN9YN3IyjfjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=778c70dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://web.archive.org/web/20171107121604/http://blog.billyau.com/posts/944</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4144/4995480912_3d92888a0e_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.static.flickr.com%2F4144%2F4995480912_3d92888a0e_b.jpg&h=bac7f183&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.macauzine.net/?action-viewnews-itemid-978-page-3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.macauzine.net%2F%3Faction-viewnews-itemid-978-page-3&d=G3JivrrVtvrQN9YN3IyjfjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=0419d174\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.macauzine.net/?action-viewnews-itemid-978-page-3</a><br />\n<br />\n傳統免治<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.macauzine.net/attachments/2016/05/2_201605111300281ab8X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.macauzine.net%2Fattachments%2F2016%2F05%2F2_201605111300281ab8X.jpg&h=72c7ff39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現在，許多澳門茶餐廳都會供應免治豬肉或牛肉飯，但做法與傳統的土生葡人免治不同，大多會加太陽蛋或三色菜。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/walkedbysio/photos/1569565486658599/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwalkedbysio%2Fphotos%2F1569565486658599%2F&d=G3JivrrVtvrQN9YN3IyjfjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=41cf91cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/walkedbysio/photos/1569565486658599/</a><br />\n<br />\n// 澳門真正特產 //<br />\n<br />\n我一直認為，真正能夠表現澳門地道風味的手信食物，並不是葡撻杏仁餅豬扒包，而是在每個澳門人心目中都有一定地位的「葡國老人牌」沙甸魚。<br />\n<br />\n這款陪伴了我們好幾十年頭的罐頭，我們稱為「辣魚」，因為其實這個牌子有好幾款味道，但我們永遠偏愛吃紅色罐的辣味。<br />\n<br />\n雖然澳門的葡國人、中國人又或中葡混血（我們稱為土生）偶有走進葡國餐廳，但影響力遠遠不及無所不在的「辣魚」。因為每家茶餐廳都有「辣魚」餐單，包括「辣魚公」(公仔麵) 「辣魚芝士多」(多士) 「辣魚菠蘿包」(港式奶油包) 等等，有時候甚至配有咖哩又或其他味道。而且每個家庭都會存有幾罐「辣魚」作為鎮廚之寶，方便隨時添餸。<br />\n<br />\n幾百年來，葡國人跟中國人表面似是互不干涉，但其實，我們生活上許多大小事的確互有感染。「辣魚」吃法演變也就是澳門殖民特色的其一小小憑證，坊間早已共融的思想行為當然也不算少。<br />\n<br />\n所以我說，「辣魚」及其系列餐單，才是澳門的真正特產，澳門的獨有風味。下次哪國親友到來，都一定要帶他試。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/rY96mS\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FrY96mS&h=75d9b5f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nChi Kei Lok 以前嘅葡國辣魚正好多，夾豬仔包超正！<br />\n<br />\n劉健城 每次過澳門探朋友 , 佢老母都會比幾罐我<br />\n<br />\nJessie Lei 宿舍有成櫃<br />\n<br />\nFelix Tam 煮出前一丁必備<br />\n<br />\n陳嘉樂 10幾蚊~澳門軟實力!!<br />\n<br />\n海闊天空 重點是每個人都吃~!!<br />\n<br />\nPenelope Puian Ng 每次番台灣必帶物品之一<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://maps.gastronomy.gov.mo/zh-hant/author/memo/memo013/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmaps.gastronomy.gov.mo%2Fzh-hant%2Fauthor%2Fmemo%2Fmemo013%2F&d=G3JivrrVtvrQN9YN3IyjfjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=500e73b9\" target=\"_blank\">http://maps.gastronomy.gov.mo/zh-hant/author/memo/memo013/</a><br />\n<br />\n辣魚芝士多<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://maps.gastronomy.gov.mo/static/MEDIA/MEMO/MEMO013/01_IMG_8162.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmaps.gastronomy.gov.mo%2Fstatic%2FMEDIA%2FMEMO%2FMEMO013%2F01_IMG_8162.JPG&h=41a2c596&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"33885f625c251ec932647e2e6fdae605b35e77b3","tid":987164,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T00:37:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}